com.google.api.gax.core

Interface PageAccessor<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<T>

    public interface PageAccessor<T>
extends Iterable<T>
    Accessor for paged results from a list API method

    This is a subclass of Iterable where iterator() returns an Iterator object with the complete listing result. If necessary it can perform more rpc calls to fetch more pages.
